OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FVets will have to publish price lists,
OL,7,Fcap prescription costs, and disclose
OL,8,Fwhether they are part of a larger
OL,9,Fgroup under government plans for the
OL,10,Fbiggest shake-up of the sector in 60
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FThe package of measures is a response
OL,14,Fto an investigation by the Competition
OL,15,Fand Markets Authority (CMA), which
OL,16,Ffound problems in the vet sector could
OL,17,Fbe costing households up to #1 billion
OL,18,Fover five years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
