CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FThe report found that vet fees have
OL,7,Frisen at nearly twice the rate of
OL,8,Finflation, and pet owners are often
OL,9,Funaware of prices or are not given
OL,10,Festimates for treatments that can run
OL,11,Finto thousands of pounds.
OL,13,FIn a white paper published on
OL,14,FThursday, the government promised to
OL,15,Fradically modernise the industry, with
OL,16,Fa series of reforms it intends to
OL,17,Flegislate for.
OL,19,FITV News takes a look at what these
OL,20,Fchanges could mean for you and your
OL,21,Ffour-legged friends.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
