OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FWhat are the costs of owning a pet?
OL,8,FAn estimated 60% of UK households `
OL,9,Fabout 17 million ` have a pet, and the
OL,10,Fcost of owning one has risen steeply
OL,11,Fin recent years.
OL,13,FIn 2024, the most recent year for
OL,14,Fwhich figures are available, owners
OL,15,Fspent about #6.7bn on veterinary and
OL,16,Fother services, according to the CMA.
OL,17,FThis works out at about #390 a year
OL,18,Fper pet-owning household.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FThere have been growing concerns that
OL,7,Fpet owners were not always given the
OL,8,Ffull picture of the costs for services
OL,9,Fand there has been a push for a law
OL,10,Ffor vets to provide itemised bills and
OL,11,Fwritten estimates for more expensive
OL,12,Ftreatments.
OL,14,FA Which? survey last year showed that
OL,15,Fmore than 50% of pet owners consider
OL,16,Fthe price of vet care to be excessive,
OL,17,Fdespite just less than a quarter
OL,18,Fsaying they have issues with the
OL,19,Fquality of care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FSpeaking about the necessity of these
OL,7,Fchanges, Environment Secretary Emma
OL,8,FReynolds said: "Pets are part of the
OL,9,Ffamily, but for too many households,
OL,10,Fthe cost of caring for them has become
OL,11,Fa real worry.
OL,13,F"These reforms will help owners avoid
OL,14,Funexpected bills, compare prices more
OL,15,Feasily and get the best value care for
OL,16,Ftheir pets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
