OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,F"We're modernising a system that
OL,7,Fhasn't been updated for sixty years,
OL,8,Fputting pet owners first while giving
OL,9,Fvets the modern framework they need to
OL,10,Fsupport the future of the profession."
OL,12,FWhat will the government change?
OL,14,FThe white paper set out by the
OL,15,Fgovernment sets out changes to several
OL,16,Faspects of veterinary care.
OL,26,@rD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
