OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FWhen they come into force, vet
OL,7,Fpractices will be legaly required to
OL,8,Fpublish price lists for common
OL,9,Ftreatments and be transparent about
OL,10,Foptions and changes, allowing pet
OL,11,Fowners to choose the best treatment
OL,12,Ffor their animals.
OL,14,FAlongside this pet owners will be
OL,15,Fsupported by an enhanced 'Find a Vet'
OL,16,Fservice to improve choice and
OL,17,Fcompetition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FThe government also intends to cap
OL,7,Fprescription fees at #21, saying
OL,8,F"knowing key prices beforehand helps
OL,9,Fowners to choose the best value."
OL,11,FA new independent veterinary ombudsman
OL,12,Fwill also be established to give pet
OL,13,Fowners a clear and straightforward
OL,14,Froute to redress when complaints
OL,15,Fcannot be resolved directly with their
OL,16,Fpractice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
