PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FThis body will have the power to make
OL,7,Fbinding decisions, with the intention
OL,8,Fthat it will ensure disputes are
OL,9,Fresolved more quickly and fairly,
OL,10,Fincreasing consumer confidence.
OL,12,FThe White Paper also includes new
OL,13,Fproposals for veterinary businesses to
OL,14,Fbe subject to statutory regulation,
OL,15,Fincluding a mandatory licensing
OL,16,Fsystem, inspections and published
OL,17,Fcompliance reports to improve
OL,18,Faccountability.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
