PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FThe government said 60% of vet
OL,7,Fpractices are owned by non-vets, with
OL,8,Fmany operating under unclear ownership
OL,9,Fstructures.
OL,11,FUnder the new plans, vet businesses
OL,12,Fmust disclose who owns them so pet
OL,13,Fowners know if their local practice is
OL,14,Fpart of a larger chain or independent.
OL,16,FWill the reforms benefit veterinary
OL,17,Fprofessionals?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
