PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FAs part of the reforms, the government
OL,7,Fhas also announced a package of
OL,8,Fmeasures aimed at helping "improve job
OL,9,Fsatisfaction and boost retention
OL,10,Frates" within the industry.
OL,12,FThe British Veterinary Association
OL,13,F(BVA), which represents 19,000
OL,14,Fmembers, said legislative reform will
OL,15,Fhave a "significant impact on vets'
OL,16,Fdaily work," and urged vets to engage
OL,17,Fwith the proposals and share their
OL,18,Fviews via the consultation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
