FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FThe new measures will introduce legal
OL,7,Frecognition for veterinary nurses to
OL,8,Fstrengthen professional identity,
OL,9,Fhelping improve job satisfaction and
OL,10,Fboosting retention rates.
OL,12,FThe government also plans to modernise
OL,13,Fthe registration process for vets,
OL,14,Ffocusing on current competence rather
OL,15,Fthan past mistakes when assessing
OL,16,F"fitness to practice".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
