PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FDr Rob Williams, BVA President, said:
OL,7,F"Vets play a vital role in society,
OL,8,Ffrom caring for the nation's animals
OL,9,Fand supporting our farmers and food
OL,10,Fproduction, through to assisting
OL,11,Finternational trade, disease control
OL,12,Fand public health.
OL,14,F"If we're to continue delivering this
OL,15,Fwork effectively, we urgently need
OL,16,Freformed veterinary legislation, and
OL,17,Fthose changes will impact how we go
OL,18,Fabout all aspects of our work."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
