OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FUK Chief Veterinary Officer Dr
OL,12,FChristine Middlemiss said: "The
OL,13,Fveterinary profession has changed
OL,14,Fenormously over the past 60 years, but
OL,15,Fthe legislation underpinning it has
OL,16,Fnot kept pace.
OL,26,@tD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
