CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,F"This new framework will build a
OL,7,Fstronger, more resilient veterinary
OL,8,Fprofession fit to meet the needs of
OL,9,Fthe UK's animal sector whilst ensuring
OL,10,Fthe highest standards of care for our
OL,11,Fanimals."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
