OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783631508
OL,3,CWhat will the UK veterinary sector
OL,4,Creforms mean for pet owners?
OL,6,FThe CMA's Chief Executive, Sarah
OL,7,FCardell said: "We back the
OL,8,Fgovernment's proposals, which include
OL,9,Four recommendations on regulating the
OL,10,Fsector. For the first time, these
OL,11,Fproposals would ensure that vet
OL,12,Fbusinesses are accountable to an
OL,13,Findependent regulator, while offering
OL,14,Fconsumers more protection and a fairer
OL,15,Fdeal."
OL,26,@oD@OOUwD@FO]
